The paper deals with information theory and communication systems, specifically multiuser setups. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely category. The paper also involves MMSE (Minimum Mean Squared Error) and covariance, which are topics in cs.MM (Machine Learning) and cs.SI (Signal Processing). The paper also discusses interference and channels, which are relevant to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
